@apelisse I believe it is a part of https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/issues/68231.

This is necessary so that if someone wants to import only this package (should be rare?), the import path is not referred to as github.com, but as the k8s.io vanity url.
Ref: https://golang.org/doc/go1.4#canonicalimports

